SIMPLE: crabbing
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Crabbing
<hw>Crab"bing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or art of
catching crabs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Falconry)</fld> <def>The fighting of hawks with
each other.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Woolen Manuf.)</fld> <def>A process of scouring
cloth between rolls in a machine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Crabbish</ent>⟦br⟧
